description: This Chainlink VRF top 10% score Gatinho purrs with a rating of 48, and a multiplier of 3x. It has a total score of 144, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 1 for North, Stringalong for East, 5 for South, and 1 for West. Gatinho has the personality suit of punter. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/50483-17512-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Gatinho [144 Votes, Top 10% Score]
